08:00:13.979 --> 08:00:21.479
Hi, this is Tooey Sutherland.

08:00:21.540 --> 08:00:24.599
A Nightwing Guide to the Dragons of

08:00:24.599 --> 08:00:25.139
Pyrea.

08:00:25.259 --> 08:00:27.479
Sand Wings.

08:00:27.540 --> 08:00:28.979
Description.

08:00:29.040 --> 08:00:31.680
Pale gold or white scales, the color of

08:00:31.680 --> 08:00:35.639
desert sand, Poisonous barbed tail, Forked

08:00:35.639 --> 08:00:36.299
black tongues.

08:00:36.360 --> 08:00:40.200
Abilities, can survive a long time

08:00:40.200 --> 08:00:42.779
without water, poison enemies with the

08:00:42.779 --> 08:00:44.279
tips of their tails like scorpions.

08:00:44.340 --> 08:00:46.740
Bury themselves for camouflage in the

08:00:46.740 --> 08:00:47.279
desert sand.

08:00:47.340 --> 08:00:48.659
Breathe fire.

08:00:48.720 --> 08:00:50.939
Queen.

08:00:51.000 --> 08:00:53.939
Since the death of Queen Oasis, the tribe

08:00:53.939 --> 08:00:55.560
is split between 3 rivals for the

08:00:55.560 --> 08:00:56.040
throne.

08:00:56.099 --> 08:00:58.979
Sisters burn, blister, and blaze.

08:00:59.040 --> 08:01:01.500
Alliances.

08:01:01.560 --> 08:01:04.619
Burn fights alongside Skywings and

08:01:04.619 --> 08:01:05.279
Mudwings.

08:01:05.340 --> 08:01:08.700
Blister is allied with the sea wings, and

08:01:08.700 --> 08:01:11.099
Blaze has the support of most sand wings

08:01:11.099 --> 08:01:12.599
as well as an alliance with the ice

08:01:12.599 --> 08:01:13.080
wings.

08:01:13.200 --> 08:01:15.599
Mudwings.

08:01:15.659 --> 08:01:19.740
Description, thick armored brown scales

08:01:19.740 --> 08:01:21.060
sometimes with amber and gold

08:01:21.060 --> 08:01:21.779
underscales.

08:01:21.840 --> 08:01:24.779
Large flat heads with nostrils on top of

08:01:24.779 --> 08:01:25.139
the snout.

08:01:25.259 --> 08:01:28.919
Abilities, can breathe fire if warm

08:01:28.919 --> 08:01:29.220
enough.

08:01:29.279 --> 08:01:32.520
Hold their breath for up to an hour, blend

08:01:32.520 --> 08:01:34.740
into large mud puddles, usually very

08:01:34.740 --> 08:01:35.040
strong.

08:01:35.099 --> 08:01:38.400
Queen, queen moorhen.

08:01:38.520 --> 08:01:42.299
Alliances, currently allied with Burn and

08:01:42.299 --> 08:01:43.799
the Sky Wings in the Great War.

08:01:43.860 --> 08:01:46.439
Sky Wings.

08:01:46.560 --> 08:01:50.099
Description, red gold or orange scales

08:01:50.099 --> 08:01:54.180
enormous wings, abilities, powerful

08:01:54.180 --> 08:01:56.459
fighters and flyers can breathe fire.

08:01:56.520 --> 08:01:59.520
Queen, Queen Scarlet.

08:01:59.580 --> 08:02:03.479
Alliances, currently allied with burn and

08:02:03.479 --> 08:02:04.619
the mud wings in the Great War.

08:02:04.740 --> 08:02:07.500
Sea Wings.

08:02:07.560 --> 08:02:11.220
Description, blue or green or aquamarine

08:02:11.220 --> 08:02:14.700
scales, webs between their claws, gills

08:02:14.700 --> 08:02:16.979
on their necks, glow in the dark stripes

08:02:16.979 --> 08:02:18.779
on their tails, snouts, underbellies.

08:02:18.840 --> 08:02:23.099
Abilities, can breathe underwater, see in

08:02:23.099 --> 08:02:25.439
the dark, create huge waves with one

08:02:25.439 --> 08:02:26.759
splash of their powerful tails.

08:02:26.880 --> 08:02:28.560
Excellent swimmers.

08:02:28.619 --> 08:02:31.860
Queen, queen coral.

08:02:31.919 --> 08:02:35.759
Alliances, currently allied with blister

08:02:35.759 --> 08:02:36.540
in the Great War.

08:02:36.659 --> 08:02:39.299
Ice Wings.

08:02:39.360 --> 08:02:42.659
Description, silvery scales like the moon

08:02:42.659 --> 08:02:43.979
or pale blue like ice.

08:02:44.040 --> 08:02:48.000
Ridged claws to grip the ice, forked blue

08:02:48.000 --> 08:02:50.520
tongues, tails narrow to a whip thin

08:02:50.520 --> 08:02:50.759
end.

08:02:50.819 --> 08:02:54.720
Abilities can withstand subzero

08:02:54.720 --> 08:02:56.040
temperatures and bright light.

08:02:56.099 --> 08:02:58.319
Exhale a deadly, freezing breath.

08:02:58.380 --> 08:03:04.439
Queen, Queen Glacier, Alliances, currently

08:03:04.439 --> 08:03:06.360
allied with Blaze and most of the sand

08:03:06.360 --> 08:03:07.439
wings in the Great War.

08:03:07.560 --> 08:03:10.139
Rain wings.

08:03:10.200 --> 08:03:13.319
Description, scales constantly shift

08:03:13.319 --> 08:03:15.180
colors, usually bright like birds of

08:03:15.180 --> 08:03:17.340
paradise, prehensile tales.

08:03:17.400 --> 08:03:21.599
Abilities, can camouflage their scales to

08:03:21.599 --> 08:03:22.680
blend into their surroundings.

08:03:22.740 --> 08:03:25.439
Use their prehensile tales for climbing

08:03:25.439 --> 08:03:27.540
no known natural weapons.

08:03:27.599 --> 08:03:30.659
Queen, Queen dazzling.

08:03:30.720 --> 08:03:34.560
Alliances, not involved in the Great

08:03:34.560 --> 08:03:34.860
War.

08:03:34.919 --> 08:03:37.380
Night Wings.

08:03:37.439 --> 08:03:39.119
Description.

08:03:39.180 --> 08:03:41.580
Purplish black scales and scattered

08:03:41.580 --> 08:03:43.259
silver scales on the underside of their

08:03:43.259 --> 08:03:45.360
wings, like a night sky full of stars.

08:03:45.419 --> 08:03:47.459
Forked black tongues.

08:03:47.520 --> 08:03:51.840
Abilities, can breathe fire, disappear

08:03:51.840 --> 08:03:55.139
into dark shadows, read minds, foretell

08:03:55.139 --> 08:03:55.500
the future.

08:03:55.560 --> 08:03:59.220
Queen, a closely guarded secret.

08:03:59.279 --> 08:04:03.659
Alliances, too mysterious and powerful to

08:04:03.659 --> 08:04:04.439
be part of the war.
